    • Method Detail

      • parseIlstElement

        public static Metadata.Entry parseIlstElement(ParsableByteArray ilst)
        Parses a single ilst element from a ParsableByteArray. The element is read starting from the current position of the ParsableByteArray, and the position is advanced by the size of the element. The position is advanced even if the element's type is unrecognized.
        Parameters:
        ilst - Holds the data to be parsed.
        Returns:
        The parsed element, or null if the element's type was not recognized.
